FBIS4-21705 "jptot014__l94005" JPRS-TOT-94-014-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 1 April 1994 EAST ASIA JAPAN Taihikai Members Hold ASAHI SHIMBUN Employees Hostage Taihikai Members Hold ASAHI SHIMBUN Employees Hostage Gunmen Take 10 Hostages OW0104053194 Tokyo KYODO in English 0515 GMT 1 Apr 94 OW0104053194 Tokyo KYODO English BFN [Text] Tokyo, April 1 KYODO -- Two gunmen entered the Tokyo headquarters of the national daily ASAHI SHIMBUN at about 1:30 p.m. Friday [1 April] and took 10 of the company's employees hostage on the building's 15th floor, police said. Police said the gunmen were right-wingers and were also armed with a sword and dynamite. Police said one of the men had fired a shot from a gun.
